		<header>
			<h1 class="entry-title">Kolossal failure: 10 lessons I learned from burning through $50,000 on a hardware project that bombed</h1>
			<p>In this guest post, Bulgaria-based entrepreneur Ivaylo Kalburdzhiev shares his roller-coaster experience of launching a startup, named KOLOS, and the lessons he&#8217;s picked up from the failed venture.</p>
		</header>
